    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based<strong> hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Finely slice <strong>half</strong> the <strong>red onion quarters</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and set aside in a small bowl</p>",
