      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add your<strong> meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) to the dish with the <strong>red</strong> <strong>onion quarters</strong> and<strong> crushed garlic</strong></p><p>Cook for 2-3 min, breaking the meat-free mince into large chunks with a wooden spoon, until very lightly browned</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
