        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir in your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>,<strong> ras el hanout</strong>, <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[510ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, stir everything together, then put the dish in the oven for 40 min or until thickened and cooked through – this is your <strong>baked spicy meat-free mince stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632210948374-x200.jpg",
