      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, dollop your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> over the<strong> baked spicy meat-free mince stew</strong> and tear your <strong>dill</strong> and <strong>parsley</strong> all over</p><p>Top with the <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong> and serve with the <strong>warmed naan[s]</strong> to the side</p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
